metadata.name: #1 Barstow, United States
metadata.description: Do you like treasure hunts? If so, join the World's largest real-life treasure hunt. Geo Treasure Maps will help you discover hidden NFT treasures all around the World. The high-tech treasure hunt combines GPS tracking with outdoor adventure, and it's fun for all ages. The joy and rewards of discovering treasures are the bonus to a fun day spent hiking, biking, trekking, and searching in unfamiliar places with lots to discover.
